---
export const prerender = true;
---
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Persona: The User | Admin</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" />
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: Inter, system-ui, sans-serif; min-height: 100vh; background: #030712; color: #f9fafb; }
    .header { background: #111827; border-bottom: 1px solid #1f2937; padding: 16px 24px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .logo { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24, #d97706); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
    .back-link { color: #9ca3af; text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #374151; }
    .back-link:hover { color: #fbbf24; border-color: #fbbf24; }
    .container { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 32px 24px; }
    .hero { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 32px; padding: 24px; background: #111827; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid #1f2937; border-top: 3px solid #3b82f6; }
    .hero-icon { font-size: 56px; }
    .hero-name { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }
    .hero-role { font-size: 13px; color: #3b82f6; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .section { background: #111827; border: 1px solid #1f2937; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .section-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #fbbf24; margin-bottom: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
    .section p, .section li { font-size: 14px; color: #d1d5db; line-height: 1.7; }
    .section ul { padding-left: 20px; }
    .section li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .tag { display: inline-block; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 100px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; background: #1e3a5f; color: #93c5fd; margin: 2px 4px 2px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">⚙️ xConvert24 Admin</div>
    <a href="/admin/personas" class="back-link">← All Personas</a>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero">
      <div class="hero-icon">👤</div>
      <div>
        <div class="hero-name">The User</div>
        <div class="hero-role">Primary Customer</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">📋 Bio</div>
      <p>The User is xConvert24's core audience — someone who needs quick, accurate unit conversions for everyday life. They might be a student doing homework, a cook converting recipes, a traveller checking currency rates, or a professional dealing with international units. They value speed, accuracy, and simplicity.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">🎯 Goals</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Convert units quickly without signing up or paying</li>
        <li>Get accurate results they can trust</li>
        <li>Bookmark frequently-used converters for quick access</li>
        <li>Earn ConvertCoins through daily usage and streaks</li>
        <li>Discover new tools that solve adjacent problems</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">😤 Pain Points</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Ads cluttering competitor conversion sites</li>
        <li>Slow page loads when they just need a quick answer</li>
        <li>Inaccurate or outdated conversion rates</li>
        <li>Too many steps to get to the converter they need</li>
        <li>No way to save favourite conversions</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">🧭 Typical Journey</div>
      <p>Arrives via Google search ("kg to lbs") → lands on converter page → performs conversion → bookmarks page → returns next day → earns streak coins → explores other tools.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">📊 Key Metrics</div>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Conversion frequency:</strong> 2–5 conversions per visit</li>
        <li><strong>Session duration:</strong> 30 seconds to 3 minutes</li>
        <li><strong>Return rate:</strong> 40% within 7 days</li>
        <li><strong>Pages per session:</strong> 1–3</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">🏷️ Tags</div>
      <span class="tag">Organic Search</span>
      <span class="tag">Mobile-first</span>
      <span class="tag">Speed-sensitive</span>
      <span class="tag">Accuracy-focused</span>
      <span class="tag">Bookmark User</span>
      <span class="tag">Streak Builder</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
